.TH "pdc_desc_count" 9 "pdc_desc_count" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pdc_desc_count \- Count the number of DMA descriptors that will be required for a given scatterlist. Account for the max length of a DMA buffer.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "u32" pdc_desc_count
.BI "(struct scatterlist *sg "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "sg" 12
Scatterlist to be DMA'd
.SH "RETURN"
Number of descriptors required
